release_note: Added all 21 Photo Effect filters from ACDSee Photo Studio. Performance improvements and bug fixes

Access to Albums Events and Faces synced from iTunes Bug fixes stability and performance enhancements

Photos can now be captured opened and exported using the new HEIF format on supporting hardware . A Text tool has been added Edit mode. Edit mode is now 100 color managed and utilizes wide color device displays. Images can now be imported from file storage providers for editing or adding to a collage. Images can now be exported from other apps and opened in ACDSee for editing. The Collections browser has been redesigned to make it easier to locate collections and can now browse Moments. Looped animations created from Live Photos can now be played back. The Camera settings UI has been redesigned and additional settings are available. Raw capture can now be configured to produce DNG DNG JPEG or separate DNG and processed assets. Captures with adjustments can now be output as original edited assets allowing the adjustments to be modified later or the adjusted image can be output to a separate asset from the unadjusted photo. The drawer button can be long pressed to go directly to the camera settings. The output format indicator can be tapped to go directly to the photo capture settings. Startup and general operation is much faster and more stable. Numerous bug fixes stability and performance enhancements have been applied.
Fixed large images with sharpening applied not saved correctly on iOS 10
Fixed an issue with Enable volume button shutter in camera. Increased collage resolution.

Editor: Fixed brushed on focus not applied correction Fixed reduced strength effects not applied correctly on some devices Fixed Effect gradient settings not preserved when a different effect is selected Fixed brushed on frame not applied correctly Presets can now be renamed and reordered Camera: Added Video Stabilization setting Added separate buttons to Reset Capture Settings and Reset All camera settings Fixed Flash Fusion mode not saving correctly on some devices Fixed image filename sequence numbers being skipped when capturing RAW Recovery of captured video that could not be written to the device s photo library Fixed torch turned off after taking a photo with Torch Flash flash mode Collage: Added collage aspect ratio setting Added additional background color choices Don t close Collage mode after completing a save share action Don t reset the zoom and pan adjustments when the cell border size is changed General: Added Depth Effect overlay badge to thubmnails mode Fixed Live Photo badge sometimes not shown in thumbnails view Fixed some artifacts in strong highlight areas when using Dehaze Performance improvements and bug fixes Bug fixes stability and performance enhancements

Nondestructive RAW processing on supported devices The Camera now supports shooting RAW on supported devices. The Editor supports color management and wide color. The Camera now has white balance presets including a custom preset where you can store your own custom white balance setting. The Editor has a new white balance color picker that lets you correct white balance by selecting a neutral gray spot in the photo. A fantastic new Dehaze adjustment that recovers and enhances detail lost due to atmospheric haze and smudged camera lenses Redesigned Home screen devoting more space for your photos and now including a Map button to view your photos on a map Bug fixes stability and performance enhancements

Camera has a new image format setting to save as TIFF PNG or JPEG Sharpness and Denoise adjustments are now available in the camera Flash Bracketing is now supported on the front facing camera Split screen multitasking on iPad is now supported Added keyboard shortcuts for use with hardware keyboards Performance improvements and bug fixes.
Performance improvements and bug fixes. Add support for full resolution image saving.

Performance improvements and bug fixes. New info panel in view mode with histogram exposure warnings photo location map and EXIF IPTC metadata table. New map view mode for browsing photos by location. Improved support for Live Photos with commands to remove video export video and save still image. Export function with options to save photo losslessly as TIFF PNG or as JPEG with desired quality. Play animated GIFs in view mode. New effects group Love . Added stickers and frames collections.
